post.content:
Band Parents,

Don't forget Market Day Pie pickup is this Thursday, November 6, 2014 from 6:00 - 7:00 pm in Cafe #2 at the high school.

We also have 8 extra pies for sale if anyone is interested. They are:

  • Classic Apple - Qty 2
  • Pumpkin Pie - Qty 2
  • French Silk - Qty 2
  • Fruit Medley Deep Dish - Qty 2

If anyone is interested, it is first come, first serve. You can email me at suegaluska@yahoo.com or call at 440-582-4120 before 4:00 pm if you are interested. Or you can purchase whatever is still available at the Pie pick up.

Thanks, Sue Galuska
